---
title: Prosciutto Croque Madame Sandwiches with a Pickled Shallot Salad
description: This French-inspired favorite combines the best of breakfast into one creamy, dreamy sandwich. Crusty sourdough, creamy mustard sauce, savory prosciutto, and melty gouda are topped with a fried egg and grated Parmesan, then finished with chives for a pop of freshness. Accompanied by a light, citrusy salad starring pickled shallot, this sumptuous meal is fit for a queen.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prosciutto-croque-madame-sandwiches-72d51160.jpg
